FBIS3-30204 "dreeu020_s_94003" FBIS-EEU-94-020 Document Type:Daily Report 31 Jan 1994 SLOVENIA Zhirinovskiy on Private Visit to Ljubljana Asked To Leave Country AU2801194894 Ljubljana Radio Slovenia Network in Slovene 1800 GMT 28 Jan 94 AU2801194894 Ljubljana Radio Slovenia Network Language: Slovene Article Type:BFN [Text] The Foreign Ministry has, in the meantime, reported that a group of men, supporters of Vladimir Zhirinovskiy, last night gravely violated public order in Bled. The Foreign Ministry informed Yuri Stepanovich Girenko, charge d'affaires of the Russian Embassy in Ljubljana, about the event that had disturbed some of the Slovene public and advised that Vladimir Zhirinovskiy and his men leave the territory of the Republic of Slovenia as soon as possible.
